Southampton’s Mario Lemina is set to join Galatasaray on loan.

He has played 49 times for Saints since joining two years ago, scoring one goal.

Lemina was linked with Manchester United earlier in the window.

In othet news, Keylor Navas is in Paris to complete his move from Real Madrid to PSG.

The goalkeeper is set to join the Parisians with Alphonse Areola going in the opposite direction.

In the same manner, Chicharito joins Sevilla

Javier Hernandez has left West Ham for Sevilla. He moves on a permanent deal for a fee in the region of £8.6million, plus a further £900,000 in add-ons.


			
